▶ {Duj vIpaw.:sen:nolink} or {DujDaq vIpaw.:sen:nolink} (the {-Daq:n} is optional) "I arrive at the ship."[2]
▶ {DujDaq jIpaw.:sen:nolink} "I arrive on the ship."  That is, "I arrive via the ship."[2]
▶ {Qo'noSDaq paw cha' DIvI' beq.:sen}

This is one of the most common Klingon epithets.

This would normally take the suffix {-pu':n}. Using the suffix {-mey:n} adds an additional layer of insult. The resemblance to the verb {taQ:v} is coincidental.[2]

Watch Gowron say this: {YouTube video:url:http://youtu.be/GonhyphPQPU}

